ng> HTML, CSS, JavaScript.<br><strong>Backend:</strong> Python (Flask/Django), Node.js (Express.js).<br><strong>AI &amp; NLP:</strong> TensorFlow/PyTorch, OpenAI GPT, Google Cloud Speech-to-Text.<br><strong>Database:</strong> MongoDB/Firebase.<br><strong>Video Call Integration:</strong> WebRTC/Twilio.<br><strong>Multilingual Support:</strong> Google Translate/Microsoft Translator API.<br><br><strong>Challenges &amp; Solutions</strong><br><strong>User Adoption:</strong> Easy-to-use interface with tutorials in multiple languages. (still in development)<br><strong>AI Accuracy:</strong> Regular updates and validation from medical professionals.<br><br><strong>Impact &amp; Benefits</strong><br><strong>Bridging Healthcare Gaps:</strong> Provides affordable and accessible healthcare to rural populations.<br><strong>Promoting Ayurveda:</strong> Encourages holistic health solutions alongside modern medicine.<br><strong>Conclusion</strong><br>Swasthya Samvad is more than just a telemedicine platform‚Äîit is a comprehensive healthcare solution designed for accessibility, inclusivity, and affordability. By integrating real-time consultations, AI-powered assistance, and multilingual accessibility, it ensures that quality healthcare is available to all, regardless of location or literacy level.<br><br></p>
